          <p class='first-para'>
            On flexible hours, is my hon. Friend aware of the problem in the health service, where nurses work excessive hours. The trusts and private nursing homes get round the problem by
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_122wh' title='Col. 122WH &mdash; HC Deb 17 July 2002 vol 389 c122WH' name='column_122wh' href='#column_122wh' rel='bookmark'>122WH</a>
